### NetVizor API Test Cases

### Get network interfaces list - default 1 hour range
GET http://localhost:8268/api/statistics/interfaces

###

### Get network interfaces list - specify time range
GET http://localhost:8268/api/statistics/interfaces?timeRange=day

###

### Get network interfaces list - 1 week time range
GET http://localhost:8268/api/statistics/interfaces?timeRange=week

###

### Get network interfaces list - 1 month time range
GET http://localhost:8268/api/statistics/interfaces?timeRange=month

###

### Get available time ranges
GET http://localhost:8268/api/statistics/available-ranges

###

### Get traffic trends data - default 1 hour all interfaces
GET http://localhost:8268/api/traffic/trends

###

### Get traffic trends data - specify time range and interface
GET http://localhost:8268/api/traffic/trends?timeRange=1day&interfaceId=all

###

### Get traffic trends data - 1 week data
GET http://localhost:8268/api/traffic/trends?timeRange=7days&interfaceId=all

###

### Get traffic trends data - 1 month data
GET http://localhost:8268/api/traffic/trends?timeRange=30days&interfaceId=all

###

### Get top apps traffic data - default 1 hour top 10
GET http://localhost:8268/api/traffic/top-apps

###

### Get top apps traffic data - specify time range and limit
GET http://localhost:8268/api/traffic/top-apps?timeRange=1day&limit=20

###

### Get top apps traffic data - 1 week data
GET http://localhost:8268/api/traffic/top-apps?timeRange=7days&limit=15

###

### Get top apps traffic data - 1 month data
GET http://localhost:8268/api/traffic/top-apps?timeRange=30days&limit=50

###

### Get software traffic top ranking - default 1 hour page 1 100 items
GET http://localhost:8268/api/apps/top-traffic

###

### Get software traffic top ranking - specify time range and pagination
GET http://localhost:8268/api/apps/top-traffic?timeRange=1day&page=1&pageSize=50

###

### Get software traffic top ranking - page 2 data
GET http://localhost:8268/api/apps/top-traffic?timeRange=1day&page=2&pageSize=30

###

### Get software traffic top ranking - 1 week data
GET http://localhost:8268/api/apps/top-traffic?timeRange=7days&page=1&pageSize=100

###

### Get software traffic top ranking - 1 month data
GET http://localhost:8268/api/apps/top-traffic?timeRange=30days&page=1&pageSize=100
